textAnnotations.description:
SENATOR SPECTER,
DID You CHANGE PARTES
ON RINCIPLE OR TO
HELP YOUR CONSTİTUENS?
ON THE PRINCIPLE
THAT INEED HELP
WITH TOB SECURITY.
